data.description: Welcome to this charming and meticulously maintained CBS home in Jupiter, FL. Upon entering you will be greeted with natural lighting, open floor plan, and spacious living room! Just off of the main living area you will find 3 spacious bedrooms and 1 beautifully updated bathroom! Additional home features include, 2016 AC, full storm protection (accordion shutters on all windows & panels on doors), ample storage and interior laundry room! This home is situated on a large corner lot, providing endless opportunities for buyers! Bring your boat, truck and RV! Convenience is key with this home's central location. Within 5 minutes or less, you can reach Jupiter's stunning public beaches, shopping, dining, Burt Reynolds boat ramp, I-95, and the Florida Turnpike.
